Task 5: Admin panel backup settings page


**Files:**
- Create: `website/src/pages/admin/einstellungen/backup.astro`
- Create: `website/src/pages/api/admin/einstellungen/backup.ts`
- Modify: `website/src/components/AdminEinstellungenTabs.astro`

- [ ] **Step 1: Add Backup tab to AdminEinstellungenTabs.astro**

  In `website/src/components/AdminEinstellungenTabs.astro`, add to the `tabs` array (after Branding):

  ```typescript
    { href: '/admin/einstellungen/backup', label: 'Backup' },
  ```

- [ ] **Step 2: Create website/src/pages/admin/einstellungen/backup.astro**

  ```astro
  ---
  import AdminLayout from '../../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
  import AdminEinstellungenTabs from '../../../components/AdminEinstellungenTabs.astro';
  import { getSession, getLoginUrl, isAdmin } from '../../../lib/auth';
  import { getSiteSetting } from '../../../lib/website-db';

  const session = await getSession(Astro.request.headers.get('cookie'));
  if (!session) return Astro.redirect(getLoginUrl(Astro.url.pathname));
  if (!isAdmin(session)) return Astro.redirect('/admin');

  const BRAND = process.env.BRAND || 'mentolder';
  const saved = Astro.url.searchParams.get('saved') === '1';

  const uploadPath = await getSiteSetting(BRAND, 'filen_upload_path');
  const defaultPath = `/workspace-backups/${BRAND}`;
  ---

  <AdminLayout title="Backup">
    <AdminEinstellungenTabs current={Astro.url.pathname} />
    <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 640px;">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Backup</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--mute); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        Tägliche Datenbank-Backups (02:00 UTC, AES-256 verschlüsselt). Lokale Kopie auf PVC +
        Upload zu Filen WebDAV (<code style="font-size: 0.8rem;">webdav.filen.io</code>). Zugangsdaten sind als
        Kubernetes-Secret hinterlegt und hier nicht sichtbar.
      </p>

      {saved && (
        <div style="background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #86efac; font-size: 0.875rem;">
          Einstellungen gespeichert.
        </div>
      )}

      <form method="POST" action="/api/admin/einstellungen/backup">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <label style="display: block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--mute-2); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            Filen Upload-Pfad
          </label>
          <input
            type="text"
            name="filen_upload_path"
            value={uploadPath ?? defaultPath}
            placeholder={defaultPath}
            style="width: 100%; background: var(--ink-800); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.625rem 0.875rem; color: var(--fg); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem; outline: none;"
          />
          <p style="color: var(--mute); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.375rem;">
            Absoluter Pfad im Filen-Drive (muss mit / beginnen). Wird beim nächsten Backup-Lauf um 02:00 UTC wirksam.
          </p>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          style="background: var(--brass); color: var(--ink-900); border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.625rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;"
        >
          Speichern
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </AdminLayout>
  ```

- [ ] **Step 3: Create website/src/pages/api/admin/einstellungen/backup.ts**

  ```typescript
  import type { APIRoute } from 'astro';
  import { getSession, isAdmin } from '../../../../lib/auth';
  import { setSiteSetting } from '../../../../lib/website-db';

  export const POST: APIRoute = async ({ request, redirect }) => {
    const session = await getSession(request.headers.get('cookie'));
    if (!session || !isAdmin(session)) return new Response('Forbidden', { status: 403 });

    const form = await request.formData();
    const brand = process.env.BRAND || 'mentolder';

    const uploadPath = (form.get('filen_upload_path') as string)?.trim();

    if (!uploadPath || !uploadPath.startsWith('/')) {
      return new Response(JSON.stringify({ error: 'Pfad muss mit / beginnen' }), { status: 400 });
    }

    await setSiteSetting(brand, 'filen_upload_path', uploadPath);

    return redirect('/admin/einstellungen/backup?saved=1', 303);
  };
  ```

- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**

  ```bash
  git add website/src/pages/admin/einstellungen/backup.astro \
    website/src/pages/api/admin/einstellungen/backup.ts \
    website/src/components/AdminEinstellungenTabs.astro
  git commit -m "feat(website): add Backup tab to admin settings with Filen upload path editor"
  ```

